Package ie.gmit.sw

Class Menu

java.lang.Object
ie.gmit.sw.Menu
public class Menu
extends java.lang.Object
Menu allows the user to input a JAR file to be analysed. The classes in the JAR file are processed through a while loop are sent to other classes to get information and metrics on them.
Author:
William Vida
